      <strong>No,</strong> this is a common myth. Dermaplaning does not change the structure of your hair follicles. The vellus hair (peach fuzz) will grow back at the same rate and texture as before.
    </p>
    <p>
      Because we're removing vellus hair (not terminal hair like on your legs or underarms), it cannot grow back thicker or darker.
    </p>
